snippet.title: 3 AM at The Krusty Krab: Developer Commentary
snippet.description:
In today's Developer Commentary I play through 3 AM at The Krusty Krab, one of the easiest games I've ever made. But will Dave ever get over his hate for the game? Find out in this shitty video.
